WEBVTT

00:00.960 --> 00:06.040
<b>The Game of Life and How to Play it by Florence Scovel Shinn</b>

00:06.240 --> 00:09.420
<b>Chapter 1: The Game</b>

00:10.380 --> 00:15.820
<b>Most people consider a life a battle, but it's not a battle it's a game</b>

00:15.820 --> 00:23.380
<b>it is a game, however, which cannot be played successfully without the knowledge of spiritual law</b>

00:23.720 --> 00:30.620
<b>and the Old and the New Testaments give the rules of the game with wonderful clearness.</b>

00:30.620 --> 00:35.620
<b>Jesus Christ taught that it was a great game of Giving and Receiving.</b>
